Epimerites I free. Epigynum 36–40 long, 86–98 wide (
Fig. 2B
). Head of spermatheca without collar, proximal part of primary spermaduct with enlargement, secondary spermaducts 25–30 long (
Fig. 3H
). Inner margins of epimerites IIIa with narrow finger-like extension, in some specimens these extensions separated from sclerotized areas around epimerites. Epimerites IVa long. Anal opening with small adanal sclerites.
